imdb-movies-tv-shows.longDescription:
## IMDb Movies & TV Shows API

Access IMDb movie and TV show data — the world's most popular entertainment database.

### Features
- Search by title or browse curated charts: Top 250 Movies, Top 250 TV, MovieMeter, TVMeter
- Returns title, year, rating, vote count, cast, plot summary, genres, runtime, box office
- Poster images and direct IMDb links
- Up to 50 results per search, structured JSON

### Built For
Developers building movie recommendation engines, streaming content trackers, entertainment aggregators, and film analytics dashboards.

### Example Use
Query `?q=inception` → returns IMDb data including 8.8 rating, cast list, $836M box office, genres, and plot summary.

**Free tier**: 50 requests/month.

## Code Examples

### cURL
```bash
# Search for a movie by title
curl -X GET 'https://imdb-movies-tv-shows.p.rapidapi.com/imdb/search?query=the+dark+knight&limit=10' \
  -H 'X-RapidAPI-Key: YOUR_RAPIDAPI_KEY' \
  -H 'X-RapidAPI-Host: imdb-movies-tv-shows.p.rapidapi.com'
```

### Python
```python
import requests

url = 'https://imdb-movies-tv-shows.p.rapidapi.com/imdb/search'
# Search for TV shows by title
params = {
    'query': 'breaking bad',
    'limit': '10'
}
headers = {
    'X-RapidAPI-Key': 'YOUR_RAPIDAPI_KEY',
    'X-RapidAPI-Host': 'imdb-movies-tv-shows.p.rapidapi.com'
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers, params=params)
results = response.json()
for title in results.get('results', []):
    print(f"{title['title']} ({title['year']}) - {title['rating']}/10 ({title['voteCount']} votes) - {title['genres']}")
```

### JavaScript
```javascript
const options = {
  method: 'GET',
  headers: {
    'X-RapidAPI-Key': 'YOUR_RAPIDAPI_KEY',
    'X-RapidAPI-Host': 'imdb-movies-tv-shows.p.rapidapi.com'
  }
};

// Get Top 250 movies chart
fetch('https://imdb-movies-tv-shows.p.rapidapi.com/imdb/search?query=oppenheimer&limit=5', options)
  .then(res => res.json())
  .then(data => {
    data.results.forEach(movie => {
      console.log(`${movie.title} (${movie.year}) - ${movie.rating}/10 - ${movie.runtime} - Box Office: ${movie.boxOffice}`);
    });
  });
```
